snippet.title: GoldenEye With Mario Characters v3.1 - Full Livestream
snippet.description:
Streaming the latest version of GoldenEye With Mario Characters! This time it features three new custom levels plus the whole main campaign, thanks to a new menu that allows for a expanded level selection. Full game on 00 Agent as always, but I'll be using the N64 controller this time.

Download available here: https://www.moddb.com/mods/goldeneye-with-mario-characters

Emulator: 1964 GEPD - https://youtu.be/8mL0I__VMec
Capture card: AVerMedia GC573
Controller: Original N64 controller

#goldeneye #n64 #nintendo64
